Class StatisticFormats

    • Field Detail

      • COUNT

        public static StatisticFormat COUNT
        A statistic without a format.

      • DISTANCE

        public static StatisticFormat DISTANCE
        A statistic measured in centimeters, meters, or kilometers depending on the magnitude. The input is taken as centimeters with a scale of 1 block equaling 1 meter.

      • FRACTIONAL

        public static StatisticFormat FRACTIONAL
        A statistic measured in 0.1 steps.

      • TIME

        public static StatisticFormat TIME
        A statistic measured in seconds, minutes, hours, or days depending on the magnitude. The input is taken as ticks with 20 ticks equaling one second.
